{
  "text": "There are several general reviews in the literature on rehabilitation following knee arthroplasty [CITATION_1] , and considerable international research about RITH has been done over the past 10 years [CITATION_2] . Theoretical models and qualitative and quantitative studies all acknowledge the influence of the environment on functioning [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . When the activities of daily living (ADL) are carried out in the home setting, the situation is more meaningful to a patient than artificial simulations in a clinical setting [CITATION_5] .",
